   <h2 align="center">Eclipse IDE</h2>
   <hr>
   <br><br>

   <h3 align="center">Download</h3>

<p>You have to download <b>Eclipse IDE</b> from site <a target="_blank" href="http://www.eclipse.org/downloads">http://www.eclipse.org/downloads</a> 

   <h3 align="center">Installation</h3>

To installation you have to unzip the installation archive to a folder (for example, eclipse or eclipse-&lt;version&gt;.

<p>To run you have to execute file eclipse.exe (Windows) or eclipse (Linux)

<p>
